abstract: Lucie Safarova and Bethanie Mattek-Sands defeat Casey Dellacqua and Yaroslava Shvedova to win women's double title at French Open tennis tournament.
lead_paragraph: Lucie Safarova made sure she left the French Open with at least one winner’s trophy after she and Bethanie Mattek-Sands won the women’s doubles title Sunday.

headline.main: Lucie Safarova Part of Doubles Title
